<h2>Bowen Flats</h2>Visit Our Community Today!<br>2620 Bowen Rd SE<br> Washington, DC 20020<br><br> <b> <a href="#" class="show-contact" title="click to show contact info" data-href="/reply/wdc/apa/7516878411/__SERVICE_ID__" rel="nofollow">show contact info</a>
</b><br><br><b>Currently fully leased. Applications for waiting list only. Affordable Housing.</b> <br> <br>Brand New Community in Anacostia Opening Summer 2017! Bowen Flats apartment amenities include washer and dryer, complemented by plank flooring throughout and carpeted bedrooms. Each kitchen features stainless steel appliances, breakfast bar, microwave and plenty of counter space. Select apartments have balconies or a terrace. Apartments will range from one to three bedroom with sizes from 600 to 1,000 square feet. Enjoy great community amenities including an underground garage parking available for cars as well as bikes, a courtyard, resident lounge. Public transportation is easily accessible via the Anacostia Metro (Green Line Metro)and bus lines right outside your door. Income Guidelines Apply. Call for more information!
<br>
