<br><br>Pet-Policy: No pets allowed;<br><br>Lease-Length: 12-Month<br><br><br>Please call to schedule an appointment.<br> <br><b>Income Restrictions for Bowen Flats</b><br><br># Occupants   -   Max Income<br>      1 Person   -   $54,180<br>      2 People   -   $62<br>      3 People   -   $69,660<br><br><br>To qualify, annual income must be equal or below those in the chart, based on the total number of occupants. Contact the leasing office for more information.<br><br><br> <br><br>EQUAL HOUSING OPPORTUNITY<br><br><br><br>
